bnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F065731_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=db908309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋見依幾好多木嘴成日諗住求其氹嚿錢搵 IT 狗搞個網 / App 我就嬲，有冇諗過如果你嘅業務係冇 offline 成份，而諗住齋搞 tech 搵 IT 狗整個好勁嘅網或 App，咁我哋寫到嘅點解唔自己做埋佢？你估你哋啲垃圾 idea 真係好撚值錢，得你諗到，或者你好似洗米華咁大把本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我哋做 IT 狗遇到依啲 case 一向嘅做法就係一係開天價畀你，一係寫嚿垃圾畀你為咗食你嚿錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bef759395afc6abcb115d7ed2ebb4afda4f79e","tid":704844,"uid":169806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d00f1eec26610acaf768cac473768f70e2f989de","tid":704844,"uid":50564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d72d66d1ad091a8a3b5550283a74c503afde2fa","tid":704844,"uid":169806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T22:49:14.000Z","msg":"70 萬咁少其實冇乜嘢好做... 帶住70 萬過澳門過三關先再諗..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T23:05:23.000Z","msg":"我都知係少左啲嫁啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但都想學下野呀嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T23:21:30.000Z","msg":"做生意唔熟唔做， 你有咁多錢交學費不如做吓慈善，幫吓有需要嘅人..."},{"pid":"27260b427235371e17d210583dcac2be5c104139","tid":704844,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T23:22:22.000Z","msg":"得個70留番m記加大啦"},{"pid":"152124be850b9d35ba4afdfd013e730c254ab281","tid":704844,"uid":87598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T23:39:43.000Z","msg":"投資喺我身上，好多產品project想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11115987f3f7f7443547d83d12c6cca07a0a7ba2","tid":704844,"uid":50564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6bef759395afc6abcb115d7ed2ebb4afda4f79e","tid":704844,"uid":169806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d00f1eec26610acaf768cac473768f70e2f989de","tid":704844,"uid